cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.DS 

This paper focuses on information retrieval from textual data, specifically the construction of vocabularies and the computation of top-k keywords. This falls under the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses benchmarking of different weighting schemes and database implementations, which relates to Database Systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions text analysis algorithms, which falls under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of a tweet dataset and queries with various complexities and selectivities suggests a focus on Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses computing performance, which relates to Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
